---
title: Ragin' Cajun Pork Burger with Garlic Aioli & Kumara Wedges
description: Mix up a pork patty infused with the mild spices of Louisiana! With tender caramelised onion to add a touch of sweetness, plus a hearty side of kumara wedges, this meal packs flavour in every bite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragin-cajun-pork-burger-d7835973.jpg
